title: Early Bird gets the..Checkmate? :)
description:
#agadmator Let's see how Black Death plays with the black pieces :)

Henry Edward Bird vs Joseph Henry Blackburne
"Bird Without a Nest" (game of the day Dec-07-2007)
London (1886), London ENG 
Bird Opening: From Gambit. Mestel Variation (A02)

1. f4 Notes by Blackburne. 1... e5 2. fe5 d6 3. ed6 Bd6 4. Nf3 Nf6 5. d4 Ng4 6. Bg5 f6 7. Bh4 g5 8. Bf2 Nf2 9. Kf2 g4 10. Nh4 f5 11. g3 f4 12. Qd3 O-O 13. Qb3 Mr. Bird and I played many games at this opening, and many followed the same lines. 13... Kh8 14. Kg1 Qf6 15. Bg2 fg3 Stronger than Qxd4+. 16. hg3 Qf2 17. Kh2 Rf3
